description: GIS/Mapping Connector Service - AGENT-DATA-006. Monitors geospatial format parsing, spatial queries, geocoding, CRS transformations, layer management, and feature processing for the GreenLang Climate OS GIS data connector layer.

panels.description: Total number of GIS operations processed across all formats and operation types
panels.title: Total Operations

panels.description: Number of active geospatial layers currently loaded and being managed
panels.title: Active Layers

panels.description: Total number of geospatial features processed across all layers
panels.title: Total Features

panels.description: Percentage of geospatial queries served from cache (hits / (hits + misses)). Higher is better.
panels.title: Cache Hit Rate

panels.description: Current rate of processing errors across all GIS operations. Any sustained error rate requires investigation.
panels.title: Error Rate

panels.description: Rate of geospatial format parse operations per second, broken down by format (GeoJSON, Shapefile, KML, GML, WKT, GeoPackage, etc.)
panels.title: Parse Rate by Format

panels.description: Parse duration percentiles (p50, p95, p99) across all geospatial formats. SLO target: p95 < 5s.
panels.title: Parse Duration

panels.description: Distribution of geospatial file formats processed by the GIS connector (GeoJSON, Shapefile, KML, GML, WKT, GeoPackage, etc.)
panels.title: Format Distribution

panels.description: Rate of spatial queries per second, broken down by query type (intersect, within, contains, nearest, buffer, etc.)
panels.title: Spatial Query Rate

panels.description: Spatial query duration percentiles (p50, p95, p99). SLO target: p95 < 10s.
panels.title: Query Duration p50/p95/p99

panels.description: Distribution of spatial query types (intersect, within, contains, nearest, buffer, union, difference, etc.)
panels.title: Query Types

panels.description: Rate of geocoding requests per second, broken down by status (success, failure, partial)
panels.title: Geocoding Requests

panels.description: Rate of boundary resolution operations per second, broken down by boundary type (administrative, postal, census, custom)
panels.title: Boundary Resolutions

panels.description: Rate of coordinate reference system (CRS) transformations per second, broken down by source and target CRS (EPSG codes)
panels.title: CRS Transformations

panels.description: Total number of geospatial layers by status (active, processing, idle, error)
panels.title: Layer Count

panels.description: Number of features per geospatial layer. Layers with high feature counts may require optimization or partitioning.
panels.title: Features per Layer

panels.description: Table showing current layer details including name, format, feature count, status, and last update time
panels.title: Layer Status

panels.description: Rate of errors per second, broken down by operation type (parse, spatial_query, geocoding, crs_transform, layer_processing)
panels.title: Error Rate by Operation

panels.description: Distribution of errors by type (format_invalid, projection_error, geometry_invalid, timeout, connection, out_of_memory, unsupported_format)
panels.title: Error Types

panels.description: Table showing recent error details by operation, error type, and count for identifying the most problematic areas
panels.title: Error Details
